The paper discusses data anonymization, which is a topic that falls under the sub-categories of computer security (cs.CR), databases (cs.DB), and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also introduces measures of disclosure risk and information loss, which are related to information theory (cs.IT) and computational complexity (cs.CC).
